>> course: cocktail

Place some @demerara sugar{} on a plate. Moisten the rim of the #tumbler glass{} with a little water and coat the glass with the sugar
Combine @fireball whiskey{45%ml}, @vodka{15%ml}, @ground cinnamon{0.25%tsp}, a dash of @vanilla extract{} and @ice cubes{6} to a #shaker and shake for 10 seconds
Serve in the prepared glass with a @cinnamon quill{}
